{"tid":300920,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分咗手就知根本無忽冷忽熱呢個狀態","createTime":"2017-06-28T09:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T10:27:30.000Z","uid":123175,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"728fcdb8ab195974d1410b19862cd00a135f15c5","tid":300920,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"話說小弟半年前變返個毒撚<br />\n但同ex仲久唔久有keep contact<br />\n<br />\n最近小弟發現原來我ex同我contact嘅頻率<br />\n一齊前同分手後都基本上一樣<br />\n不過以前有幻想就會覺得佢係「忽冷忽熱」<br />\n而家醒覺咗佢根本就wfc我<br />\n<br />\n所以「忽冷忽熱」呢個狀態只係班毒撚嘅主觀希望<br />\n實際上係唔存在嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都on9嘅，抵你做返毒撚"},{"pid":"664beb2c319d75693ac375a2eb1c7a99a37775cf","tid":300920,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddac3e8d4e0abe3c1eb46805028498fc12a51d5","tid":300920,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"毒撚不敢面對"}]}